ZH: 这块土地很肥沃。
EN: This land is very fertile.

ZH: 我们家后面有一大片土地。
EN: There is a large piece of land behind our house.

ZH: 在农村，土地是最宝贵的资源之一。
EN: In the countryside, land is one of the most valuable resources.

ZH: 这片土地已经被开发成了一座大型公园。
EN: This land has been developed into a large park.

ZH: 农民靠种地来谋生。
EN: Farmers make a living by farming the land.

ZH: 这片土地的所有权归政府所有。
EN: The ownership of this land belongs to the government.

ZH: 他们建了一个小木屋在土地上。
EN: They built a small cabin on the land.

ZH: 这个项目将占用大片土地。
EN: This project will occupy a large area of land.

ZH: 这里的土地非常干燥。
EN: The land here is very dry.

ZH: 许多人都在争夺这块宝贵的土地。
EN: Many people are competing for this valuable land.

ZH: 这块土地上有很多果树。
EN: There are many fruit trees on this land.

ZH: 这块土地有很好的景色。
EN: This land has a beautiful view.

ZH: 农民会在土地上种植玉米和小麦。
EN: Farmers will plant corn and wheat on the land.

ZH: 土地的价格在不断上涨。
EN: The price of land is constantly rising.

ZH: 这片土地上有很多民间传说。
EN: There are many folk legends about this land.

ZH: 社会对土地资源的使用必须要有规划。
EN: Society must have a plan for the use of land resources.

ZH: 这个城市的土地质量很好。
EN: The land quality in this city is very good.

ZH: 这块土地受到了强烈的震动。
EN: This land experienced a strong earthquake.

ZH: 城市化进程导致大量土地被开发。
EN: The process of urbanization has led to the development of a large amount of land.
